l9-result9]\\\\n\\\\n### Next Steps:\\\\n1. Analyze the behavior of the `separability_matrix` function for nested CompoundModels.\\\\n2. Identify the location of the bug in the code.\\\\n3. Implement a fix to correct the computation.\\\\n4. Update tests to validate the fix.\\\"}\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\"}],\"type\":\"ToolCallRequestEvent\"},{\"id\":\"ac9fb2d5-74a6-4157-b694-1b28c80a6cd1\",\"source\":\"ProjectManager\",\"models_usage\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-05T15:58:20.141742Z\",\"content\":[{\"content\":\"Access denied - path outside allowed directories: /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-centralize/bugs/separability_matrix_issue.md not in /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_ubzgPwUOAWUtIYrqEtqX1LbV\",\"is_error\":false}],\"type\":\"ToolCallExecutionEvent\"}]},\"name\":\"ProjectManager\"}", "sender": "ProjectManager_e6524bea-c0f6-4f60-b3b7-70b7550a5a2a/e6524bea-c0f6-4f60-b3b7-70b7550a5a2a", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
