_model6-result6]\\\\n- astropy/modeling/tests/test_separable.py::test_separable[compound_model9-result9]\\\\n\\\\n### Next Steps:\\\\n1. Analyze the behavior of the `separability_matrix` function for nested CompoundModels.\\\\n2. Identify the location of the bug in the code.\\\\n3. Implement a fix to correct the computation.\\\\n4. Update tests to validate the fix.\\\"}\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\"},{\"id\":\"call_4AzIS2nkoz3lqp2QYsfUW4zU\",\"arguments\":\"{\\\"path\\\": \\\"separability_matrix_next_steps.md\\\", \\\"content\\\": \\\"## Next Steps\\\\n1. **Analyze Behavior:**  Review how `separability_matrix` handles nested CompoundModels and simulate the case in debug mode.\\\\n2. **Identify Bug:** Identify potential flaws in the current implementation that lead to incorrect results. \\\\n3. **Implement Fix:** Make necessary code changes to resolve the issue.\\\\n4. **Update Tests:** Ensure tests reflect the change and validate correctness.\\\"}\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\"}],\"results\":[{\"content\":\"Access denied - path outside allowed directories: /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-centralize/separability_matrix_issue_description.md not in /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_qrfodhwzEnb14ywVQZLZPMqs\",\"is_error\":false},{\"content\":\"Access denied - path outside allowed directories: /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-centralize/separability_matrix_next_steps.md not in /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board\",\"name\":\"board_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_4AzIS2nkoz3lqp2QYsfUW4zU\",\"is_error\":false}]},\"inner_messages\":[{\"id\":\"ca648836-4b9d-40ad-8879-447e9cf92f8c\",\"source\":\"ProjectManager\",\"models_usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":2474,\"completion_tokens\":486},\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-05T15:58:34.905356Z\",\"content\":[{\"id\"