YnOtT", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\":\"bug_report.md\",\"content\":\"## Issue:  Incorrect Separability Matrix for Nested CompoundModels\\n\\n### Description\\nThe `separability_matrix` does not compute separability correctly for nested CompoundModels. For example, the expected result of the separability matrix for a nested compound model is not achieved, resulting in misleading separation indicators.\\n\\n### Failures and Tests\\n- The issue has caused `test_separable[compound_model6-result6]` and `test_separable[compound_model9-result9]` to fail.\\n- It appears that there is an unexpected behavior when combining a basic compound model with others, leading to incorrect values in the output matrix. \\n\\n### Proposed Short-term Solution\\nTo fix this, we need to:\\n1. Analyze how the `separability_matrix` function treats nested CompoundModels.\\n2. Identify the root cause of the issue in the implementation.\\n3. Modify the code to correctly compute separability for nested structures.\\n4. Write additional tests to verify this behavior post-fix.\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}]}}], "created": 1777996722, "model": "gpt-4o-mini-2024-07-18", "object": "chat.completion", "service_tier": "default", "system_fingerprint": "fp_b6580bbee1", "usage": {"completion_tokens": 228, "prompt_tokens": 3574, "total_tokens": 3802, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": 0, "audio_tokens": 0, "reasoning_tokens": 0, "rejected_prediction_tokens": 0}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": 0, "cached_tokens": 3456}}}, "prompt_tokens": 3574, "completion_tokens": 228, "agent_id": "ProjectManager_e6524bea-c0f6-4f60-b3b7-70b7550a5a2a/e6524bea-c0f6-4f60-b3b7-70b7550a5a2a"}
