rue, False, False],\\n       [ True,  True, False, False],\\n       [False, False,  True,  True],\\n       [False, False,  True,  True]])\\n```\\n\\n### Fail-to-pass tests:\\n- astropy/modeling/tests/test_separable.py::test_separable[compound_model6-result6]\\n- astropy/modeling/tests/test_separable.py::test_separable[compound_model9-result9]\\n\\n### Next Steps:\\n1. **Analyze Behavior:**  Review how `separability_matrix` handles nested CompoundModels and simulate the case in debug mode.\\n2. **Identify Bug:** Identify potential flaws in the current implementation that lead to incorrect results. \\n3. **Implement Fix:** Make necessary code changes to resolve the issue.\\n4. **Update Tests:** Ensure tests reflect the change and validate correctness.\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}], "content": null}, {"content": "Access denied - path outside allowed directories: /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-centralize/nested_compound_model_issue.md not in /Users/cerberose/Work/mas-evaluate-pipeline/runs/example-study/mas_centralize/astropy__astropy-12907/repeat_1/project_board", "role": "tool", "tool_call_id": "call_vYNTBGETMe4E0QqcRK4tb1uB"}], "response": {"id": "chatcmpl-DcCSakTBJXf27TubePDjY5c27tsJg", "choices": [{"finish_reason": "tool_calls", "index": 0, "logprobs": null, "message": {"content": null, "refusal": null, "role": "assistant", "annotations": [], "audio": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_vRTpAbMvY0ugwDUW9idyHx3p", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\":\"nested_compound_model_bug_report.md\",\"content\":\"## Issue: Incorrect Separability Matrix in Nested CompoundModels\\n\\n### Issue Summary\\n- `separability_matrix` returns unexpected results for nested CompoundModels, indicating incorrect separability between model components that should be independent.\\n\\n### Steps to Reproduce\\n1. Import necessary components:\\n   ```python\\n   from astropy.modeling import models as m\\n   from astropy.modeling.separable import separabi